Package: typethis
Type: Package
Title: Static Type Checking for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A gradual type checking system for R that provides static analysis
    without code execution. Supports type inference, data.table types, and integrates
    with RStudio. Inspired by mypy for Python.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
